    "body": "in one sentence, the question is why EIP-2930 access list tx does NOT use the EIP-155 way of signature (for replay-attack mitigation) just as legacy tx does, the comment in the code https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/commit/bbfb1e4008a359a8b57ec654330c0e674623e52f#diff-58204a02692cd9ef1cf0767b18dbc4df99eb678126c8982350e5b727af075b5eR194-R197 only states the fact but gives no reasoning/explanation",
